sub_title: Global Director Strategic Accounts / Strategy and Execution / Commercial Transformation / Financial Services / Trade Finance
summary:
An entrepreneurial and experienced business development specialist with a proven track record in designing and optimizing result driven organizations and realizing (greenfield) projects. 

Possesses a keen understanding of the FS and the innovative tech markets and has the ability to create the teams and the commercial portfolios to succeed in constantly changing business environments. 

A customer focused team player who delivers outstanding results by optimizing the commitment of all stakeholders involved. 

Dedicated and reliable with the determination and drive required to succeed.
